Package: planscanR
Title: Retrieve Environmental-Assessment Records From European Portals
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Bart", "Hoekstra", email = "mail@barthoekstra.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A unified R interface for fetching environmental-assessment
    records (EIA, SEA, follow-up advice) from European national portals,
    with built-in tools to score records by topic relevance and select the
    ones worth a closer look. Handlers ship for the Netherlands (Commissie
    m.e.r.), Germany (UVP-Verbund), and Austria (Umweltbundesamt UVP-DB).
    Developed for the BIOGAIN project to support Net Biodiversity Gain in
    spatial energy planning.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/barthoekstra/planscanR,
